    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been totally babied and is ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
