    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR, preserved in its original factory configuration. This specimen features the legendary 4G63 inline-four, exhibiting optimal compression and a bone-dry head gasket. The MHI TD05HR-16G6C-10.5T twin-scroll turbocharger delivers instantaneous spool with zero shaft play. The drivetrain is anchored by the MR-exclusive 6-speed close-ratio manual and the sophisticated Active Center Differential (ACD), ensuring razor-sharp yaw control. The chassis remains structurally flawless, riding on original Bilstein monotube dampers and forged BBS wheels. Every bushing, seal, and synchro performs as it did on the showroom floor. A rare opportunity to acquire a performance icon with zero mechanical compromise.",
